Question 1. Identify where maven will expect the source code would be present.
	    /src/main/java/sample source code is in this package

	
Question 2. Identify where maven will expect the resources would be present.
            /src/main/resources all the resource needed to build a package

	
Question 3. Identify where maven will expect the test cases would be present.
            /src/test/java/com/sample test case are present here.


Question 4. Identify where maven will expect the compiled code would be present.
	    /tar/get/classes/com/sample


Question 5. Identify where maven will generate the artifact.
            /target/spring3hibernateapp.war
